Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something, Ivica?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say after making me wait for you, Blanc?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government is still trying to haggle with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're afraid of us foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a private company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sites have always looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fate of the survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for the girl with turquoise hair to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could stop this tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to count the dead in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why we—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are they flying so low?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to be in trouble when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go. We have our own duties to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. We don't have time to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's human nature to keep waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for the dove to return with a branch of hope in its beak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like the world was going to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's for better or worse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your inhaler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could my body be anymore inconvenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you're having these dreams because of your spiritual powers?{yuta are okinawan shamans}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not even sure that it's going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why bother taking Noah to a safer spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a fire! How can I watch him die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He barely settled in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no friends or family. I can't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, you understand that feeling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gathered all the sea mangoes for Mr. Wong yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But poaching is still poaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Just don't pass out, or the leeches are going to suck you dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come back on time, I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hundred thousand for delivering the IFO's ECU is easy money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Gazelle, are you sure it's a good idea to trust the Japanese army?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they gave you that weird gadget as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they just playing you for a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went over this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the newest beacon controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this is online, the Japanese army will lead us safely and soundly to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more concerned with what they didn't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys aren't interested, feel free to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep all the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What happened, Gazelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, but something's on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my generator's blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to land. Keep a lookout for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fuck are you doing here, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You nearly killed me because you can't drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a terrible driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.62,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to deal with kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do if the cargo gets damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't even see a cent of our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a transmitter on the case, the Japanese army will wonder why we opened it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese army?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Pippo. We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky. If we weren't in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck here, Gazelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen an ECU act like this. I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your job to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easier said than done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the kid who lives at Fukai's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mind lending me an FP?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have some spares laying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, since he has the money to \Nraise some random foreign kid and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ECU!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ECU suddenly—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stare at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "what"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've learned about this in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Scub Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it. Our FPs—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazelle! Hey, Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing! We should run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could turn into an ugly mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may have been an ugly mess all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already done with today's data...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's time to scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you call on another team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should let the kids rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a Scub Coral signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That happens all the time, Rebecka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but take a look at the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral signal that we detected 30 minutes ago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,grew rapidly in the past five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still analyzing the data,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's telling us that the probability of a Secret emerging is 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is probably where it will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. An area claimed by both the United Okinawan Archipelago and China-Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A problematic place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand now? Will you go if there's a dispatch order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to meet up with the Japanese army if we get caught up in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that light was emitted by a Scub emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should withdraw for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who would be happy with a giant that can't be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should believe in the people of Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a feeling of sadness is plaguing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat. All residents in the Osaki area of Iwato Island must evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay tuned for further updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that thing earlier was really a G-Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. What should I tell Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Central Hospital called. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be back until tomorrow morning, so go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is your entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the responsibility of a parent to send their children to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they are not bound by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, will you take my FP?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is an old man like me going to drive that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned into a real mess, so I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believed you will deliver it as agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Japs, we keep our words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prickly words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, there seems to be something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this is stuff you'd eat at a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's changing about me is this uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does it feel like something is coming to an end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to eat your words, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get back within six hours, the money's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You sound like you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've nursed me yourself if you were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your old man wouldn't give me a break if I went over to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's always your excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what your mom did,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ao. It's pointless to worry about all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm different...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you're a foreigner, but nobody's going to die because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about how much better you are compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No "buts".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough. I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. I can never win an argument against her since she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she'll cheer up when I give her this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we have much of a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a freaking huge hole in the \Nground where it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid was here, right? Fukai's kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if that foreigner kid picked it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were delivering the cargo. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the Scub popped up along with a G-Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Japs deployed their army FPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we got up caught in something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try listening to the sounds around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hear a single bird or even a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like that! Everyone smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naru! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.68,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuu, be a good girl and look at the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub shouldn't show up twice at the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than one pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you to leave the first one alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was most certainly unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting mankind from emerging unknown creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the job of our company, Generation Blue and our team Pied Piper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll dispatch your team of aces for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite the exceptional case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, I would like to discuss the price as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've yet to sign a contract and he's moving in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the chief thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,680)}And even if we rushed there now, we \Nwouldn't make it to the Secret in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if something \Nhappens to the kids in a pointless fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, I'm more worried \Nabout the children of Iwato Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All circuits are busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The internet doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get away from the Scub! Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A G-Monster could show up any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same one from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... This can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't make up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing... That damned thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's wrong with this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why is this... glowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had it after all, foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0100,,I don't know what this is, but I'm not handing it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not handing it over to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the light he discovered through fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he found the feelings his mother left for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ao finds himself in the midst of a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he encounters an anthropomorphic weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he see in this vibrating storm of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Eureka Seven AO episode 2: \NCall It What You Want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.83,0:24:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voice of the children of the stars.
